Date: Tue, 16 Feb 2010 11:24:14 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 4/5] da8xxfb.c: Corrected the da8xx FB parameters for da850/omap-l138

Original codes from TI Linux Platform Support Package
DaVinci-PSP-SDK-03.20.00.12.tgz http://software-dl.ti.com/dsps/
dsps_public_sw/sdo_sb/targetcontent/psp/DaVinci-PSP-SDK/03_20/index_FDS.html

The vfp and the vbp parameters were needed to be modified for
LK043T1DG01 display panel. Without this modification, the first
line would be cropped and not be visible on the display.

Signed-off-by: Madhvapathi Sriram <sriram.m@ti.com>
Integrated-by: Stanley.Miao <stanley.miao@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c |    4 ++--
 1 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c b/drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c
index da341df..0f307d2 100644
--- a/drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c
+++ b/drivers/video/da8xx-fb.c
@@ -191,8 +191,8 @@ static struct da8xx_panel known_lcd_panels[] = {
 		.hfp = 2,
 		.hbp = 2,
 		.hsw = 41,
-		.vfp = 2,
-		.vbp = 2,
+		.vfp = 3,
+		.vbp = 3,
 		.vsw = 10,
 		.pxl_clk = 7833600,
 		.invert_pxl_clk = 0,
